    "description": "<div style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:1.6;color:#222;max-width:800px;margin:0 auto\" vocab=\"https://schema.org/\" typeof=\"Product\">\n  <div style=\"display:none\"><span property=\"description\">Fix your old paracord bracelet with the 48pc ASR Outdoor Paracord Bracelet Buckle Set! This set comes with 48 paracord bracelet buckles in standard black. Each buckle is .5&quot; wide (15mm), making it perfect for smaller paracord bracelets. Other great uses for these buckles are camping and hiking gear repair, accessories, crafting and hobbies.</span></div>\n  <div style=\"background:#f5f5f5;padding:12px 15px;border:1px solid #e5e5e5;margin:0 0 16px\">\n    <div style=\"font-size:18px;font-weight:bold;margin-bottom:6px\">Deals Only Web Store</div>\n    <div style=\"font-size:13px\">\n      <a href=\"https://www.ebay.com/str/dealsonlywebstore\" style=\"text-decoration:none;color:#333\">Our Store</a>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n  <h2 style=\"font-size:22px;margin:0 0 12px\">ASR Outdoor Paracord Bracelet Side Release Buckle Multipack Set 15mm 20mm</h2>\n  <p>Fix your old paracord bracelet with the 48pc ASR Outdoor Paracord Bracelet Buckle Set!</p>\n  <h3 style=\"font-size:18px;margin:18px 0 8px\">Key Features</h3>\n  <ul style=\"padding-left:20px;margin:0 0 16px\">\n    <li><strong>HIGH QUALITY PLASTIC:</strong> Universal side release replacement snap buckles made to withstand longtime wear and tear</li>\n    <li><strong>MULTI FUNCTION:</strong> Snap release buckles are great for easy one-handed release and no accidental uncoupling</li>\n    <li><strong>SIZE SPECIFICATION:</strong> Overall width for webbing is 15mm or 20mm</li>\n    <li><strong>FIX REPLACE UPGRADE:</strong> Side release buckles for all nylon webbing applications including tactical paracord bracelet, backpack straps, fanny packs and dog collars</li>\n    <li>Great for outdoor use, gear repair, crafting, hobbies and more</li>\n  </ul>\n  <p style=\"text-align:center;margin:0 0 16px\"><img src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/DOWS_products/1000x1000/sports_outdoors/paracord-buckles-black-24pk-no-logo.jpg\" alt=\"Fix your old paracord bracelet with the 48pc ASR Outdoor Paracord Bracelet Buckle Set\" style=\"max-width:100%;width:600px;height:auto\"></p>\n  <h3 style=\"font-size:18px;margin:18px 0 8px\">Product Specifications</h3>\n  <ul style=\"padding-left:20px;margin:0 0 16px\">\n    <li><strong>MPN:</strong> 37404</li>\n    <li><strong>UPC:</strong> 749060377089</li>\n  </ul>\n  <p>This set comes with 48 paracord bracelet buckles in standard black. Each buckle is either 15mm or 20mm wide, making it perfect for smaller paracord bracelets.</p>\n  <p>Other great uses for these buckles are camping and hiking gear repair, accessories, crafting and hobbies.</p>\n  <p style=\"text-align:center;margin:16px 0 0\"><img src=\"https://s3.us-east-1.amazonaws.com/DOWS_photobucket/Shopify_Prop65graphic.jpg\" alt=\"California Proposition 65 warning\" style=\"display:block;margin-left:auto;margin-right:auto\" height=\"78\" width=\"273\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:18px 0 0;padding-top:12px;border-top:1px solid #e5e5e5;font-size:13px;color:#777;text-align:center\">&copy; 2026 Deals Only Web Store</p>\n</div>",
